               I did a lot of research on weapons and am currently useing a Wurrmy in primary and a Lammy secondary. Is this a good combo and how long will it be good for?<br>
              I have seen alot of posts saying to keep all your weapons skills up. How the heck can you do that? I have my 1 hd slashing up and have been trying to keep my two hand slash up but I hardly ever hit with two hand and feel like I am not contributing to the group. And although I feel like i do a good amount of damge with Dual wield I still miss alot(why is that) How could I possibly keep others up (IE pierce and two hand)<br>
             I also wanted to ask about aggro. it seems in our group in Paludal that our cleric is always getting aggro and dieing. I use taunt and it does not seem to work well. I just got the Lamentation does that help you hold aggro and what else can I do to keep the cleric alive.<br>
            As you can see I am struggling with my Warrior and any help is appreciated. I hear people say Warrior is an easy char to play. It may be, but it is a hard char. to play effectively.<br>
<br>
